 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ipAddress":"127.0.0.1","createdAt":"2026-03-20T19:10:41.226Z"},{"id":3,"userId":1,"action":"Password reset via forgot-password flow","device":null,"ipAddress":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-20T19:10:32.115Z"}]
